---
title: Grilled Maple-Chipotle Bacon-Wrapped Chicken with Elotes-Inspired Corn and Grilled Veggies
description: Fire up the grill! This dinner is chock full of incredible flavours — lime, chipotle and maple — to up the ante on chicken, veggies, sweet potatoes and corn. Word of warning: There probably won't be any leftovers.
